00:06:26,070 --> 00:06:29,070
-He's over there! -I'm sorry.

88
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:30,570
Gosh.

89
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:35,670
Hey! Cool kid!

90
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:38,170
You look like an Ostrich.

91
00:06:38,170 --> 00:06:40,070
