00:12:57,520 --> 00:13:00,320
Bunta Kuniyoshi?

214
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:03,320
Ah, that's right.

215
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,120
Well, then how does he become

216
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:09,220
the circle, cross, triangle and square?

